      <div class="card-content__text">
        <h1 class="card-content__title">Oligarchy</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Oligarchy is a form of power structure in which power actually rests with a small number of people. These people might be distinguished by nobility, wealth, family ties, education or corporate, religious or military control.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oligarchy">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/oligarchy">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content__img">
        <img class="card-content__img-pic" src="../images/idea/oligarchy.jpeg" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="card">
