      <div class="card-content__text">
        <h1 class="card-content__title">Plutocracy</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Plutocracy or plutarchy, is a form of oligarchy and defines a society ruled or controlled by the small minority of the wealthiest citizens.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plutocracy">Wikipedia</a></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content__img">
