        <h1 class="card-content__title">The Philosopher King</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">According to Plato, a Philosopher king is a ruler who possesses both a love of knowledge, as well as intelligence, reliability, and a willingness to live a simple life.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philosopher_king">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/philosopher-king">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
