        <h1 class="card-content__title">Monarchy</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">A monarchy is a form of government in which a group, usually a family called the dynasty, embodies the country's national identity and one of its members, called the monarch, exercises a role of sovereignty.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monarchy">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/monarchy">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
