        <h1 class="card-content__title">Capitalism</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Capitalism is an economic system based on private ownership of the means of production and their operation for profit. Characteristics central to capitalism include private property, capital accumulation, wage labor, voluntary exchange, a price system, and competitive markets.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Capitalism">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/capitalism">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content__img">
