      <div class="card-content__text">
        <h1 class="card-content__title">Socialism</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Socialism is a range of economic and social systems characterised by social ownership and democratic control of the means of production; as well as the political ideologies, theories, and movements that aim to establish them. Social ownership may refer to forms of public, collective, or cooperative ownership; to citizen ownership of equity; or to any combination of these.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Socialism">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/socialism">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p003k9jg">Podcast on Marx</a></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content__img">
        <img class="card-content__img-pic" src="../images/idea/socialism.jpeg" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="card">
