      <div class="card-content__text">
        <h1 class="card-content__title">Communism</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Communism is the social, political, and economic ideology and movement whose ultimate goal is the establishment of the communist society, which is a socioeconomic order structured upon the common ownership of the means of production and the absence of social classes, money, and the state.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communism">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/communism">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
      </div>
