        <h1 class="card-content__title">Conservatism</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Conservatism as a political and social philosophy promotes retaining traditional social institutions in the context of culture and civilization. Conservatives seek to preserve institutions like the Church, monarchy and the social hierarchy, as they are, emphasizing stability and continuity, while others, called reactionaries, oppose modernism and seek a return to "the way things were".</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conservatism">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/conservatism">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
