        <h1 class="card-content__title">Liberalism</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Liberalism is a political philosophy or worldview founded on ideas of liberty and equality. Whereas classical liberalism emphasises the role of liberty, social liberalism stresses the importance of equality.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberalism">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/liberalism">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
