      <div class="card-content__text">
        <h1 class="card-content__title">Libertarianism</h1>
        <p class="card-content__description">Libertarianism is a collection of political philosophies that uphold liberty. Libertarians seek to maximize autonomy and freedom of choice, emphasizing the value of political freedom, voluntary association, and the importance of individual judgment. Libertarians generally share a skepticism of authority; however, they diverge on the scope of their opposition to existing political and economic systems.</p>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Libertarianism">Wikipedia</a></h5>
        <h5 class="card-content__site"><a href="https://www.britannica.com/topic/libertarianism-politics">ENCYCLOPÆDIA BRITANNICA</a></h5>
